## 0. Preamble (v1.1 amendment)

v1.0 em ship turn 54 cross-reference 3 SPEC Kim + boi_surface_delta + RUNTIME_DEPENDENCY_CENSUS. Sau v1.0 sealed (commit 7fcdc88), Thiên Lớn ship 4 SPEC split detail cụ thể hơn vào `docs/specs/kim kernel/`.

**Conflict đáng chú ý v1.0 vs 4 split:**
- v1.0 em: W0-W4 (5 waves). W3 per-cell kernel, W4 Node retire.
- 4 split Thiên: W0-W3 (4 waves). W3 Node retire by cluster (kernel cluster trước, business sau).

Em align Thiên. Lý do: Thiên architect primary, 4 split chi tiết buildable, W0-W3 clean hơn, Thiên **ship quyền Băng veto** §4.

**Scope v1.1:** overview + cross-link 4 split + Kim state reference + authority scope + W-model align Thiên.

