Detail primary: **`spec_host_authority_runtime_v1.0_split.na`** (Thiên).

Overview ngắn:
- Binary: `nauion-host` (Rust)
- Source: `runtime/nauion-host/`
- Exec: `bin/nauion-host`
- Frame: **NDJSON Stage 1 only** (amend v1.0: drop MessagePack mention, Thiên strict Stage 1 NDJSON)
- Audit log: `logs/host-audit.ndjson` (Thiên thêm)
- Execution flow 7 steps: xem Thiên §4
- Cấm: Node deps runtime, JS eval — xem Thiên §7

